sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant API as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as KServe LLM Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Runtime as vLLM/TGI Runtime<br/>GPU Resources
    participant Route as OpenShift Route / Istio VS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant LLMServer as LLM Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>JWT Validation

    Note over User,LLMServer: Flow 3: LLM Inference Service Deployment

    User->>API: POST LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate LLMInferenceService<br/>mTLS (API Server)
    Webhook-->>API: Validated CR
    API-->>Controller: Watch Event (CR Created)

    Controller->>API: Create Deployment with vLLM/TGI Runtime<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Route/VirtualService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Controller: Resources Created

    Note over StorageInit,HFHub: Download LLM Model
    StorageInit->>HFHub: GET Model Artifacts<br/>HF Token Authentication
    HFHub-->>StorageInit: LLM Model Files (Multi-GB)
    StorageInit->>Runtime: Write to Local Storage

    Note over Runtime: Model Loading (GPU)
    Runtime->>Runtime: Load LLM into GPU Memory<br/>Node-level isolation
    Runtime-->>Runtime: Initialize vLLM/TGI Engine

    Note over User,Authorino: LLM Inference Request
    User->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3, Bearer Token
    Route->>Authorino: Validate JWT Token<br/>Authorino AuthorizationPolicy
    Authorino-->>Route: Token Valid
    Route->>LLMServer: Forward Request<br/>HTTP (mTLS if Istio)
    LLMServer->>Runtime: Generate Text<br/>Local GPU Inference
    Runtime-->>LLMServer: Generated Response
    LLMServer-->>Route: JSON Response
    Route-->>User: LLM Output
